{"tid":516134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警起出7千人戀童名冊　包括議員等知名人士","createTime":"2018-01-01T05:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T01:01:52.000Z","uid":35468,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b813a39291fbb7263b63d499eb5d2a813f1bab","tid":516134,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>蘿莉控末日！警起出名冊達7千人　不乏市議員等知名人士</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=331588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D331588&d=zz9N3OG7jFSyxGF8qp4RD9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7ff3b786\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D331588&h=19aaa3b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=331588</a><br />\n<br />\n警視廳去年5月破獲兒童色情後，起出一本客戶名冊，經過調查後發現，大約有7200人購買兒童色情刊物。其中除了名漫畫家和月伸宏之外，就連檢察官、警官、醫師或政治人物等都是常客，警方正在深入調查。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本法律規定，禁止持有兒童色情，可處1年以下有期徒刑或100萬日元的罰款。而這次起出的常客名冊裡，除眾所皆知的漫畫家和月伸宏以外，不乏各界知名人士，就連市議員也榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n警視廳將名冊中的200多人根據違反《兒童色情禁止法》函送偵辦。這次事件也是自2015年7月以後破獲最大起兒童色情案件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察！開門！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/233154_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F233154_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=53b35535&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"511fbcfbc15bc698311a5bf8f2a337a142cc7c65","tid":516134,"uid":85163,"like":13,"dislike":42,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ebc8c5f22dabf28435e3ef6787b1ae8a9211ebd","tid":516134,"uid":143499,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"香港有十一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db92403897f820ed7dbebb48db72cf6cf18a1db","tid":516134,"uid":51469,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"agentcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89d9e4b5964645477ad5f9785c24014c28dc756","tid":516134,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ffb0493ea31f0e58d42ff3d56b130fe9a14d0a","tid":516134,"uid":34223,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:21:59.000Z","msg":"湯家驊"},{"pid":"5b96e8638868435540918d07bd5412874e9f1bf5","tid":516134,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"有某個潛左出公海既連登變態佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d727bf05d1d0db097b00da5a05ff8656f09f219a","tid":516134,"uid":143499,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:15:55.000Z","msg":"日本依家好似係真人蘿莉犯法， 漫畫暫時未有規管<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心蘿莉J唔落， 罪惡感好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而想保護佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f368baaecba2c0b9e7b9c51d219853727fe51c","tid":516134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"L File <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e908f63e5d94d00318dab402b1ab9b477f7cc1","tid":516134,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"漫畫家拉左個個知<br />\n其他一係未拉 一係唔開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c748431d0920fdd611c9f49c8b1e5d6d8c5f2758","tid":516134,"uid":50801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"30e908f63e5d94d00